起初也是受到打击的。这个猜想证明对了那是一件大喜事，当然，证明错了我们也不必去嘲笑人家，因为在他之前也有很多人错了，但至少他们在思考在努力解决这个谜题，牛顿说他是站在巨人的肩膀上，其实，等到解开这个谜题的人出现时，那个人也肯定是站在巨人的肩膀上。我们不要苛求，但一定要抱有希望。一个在我们的教育体系下能这样思考很不容易，题主想上清华北大也是人之常情，谁不想呢？我想只有得到的人才有资格说不要。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560213967,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560213967","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545818878,"updated_time":1545819027,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e写在前面。希望你们指出答主没发现的问题的时候，不要对他冷嘲热讽。他只是年少轻狂了一下。就当做像自己证错了一道普通题被别人指出了错误一样吧。我觉得答主万一错了也可以这么想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然如果答主真的证出来了。。那以上全当我放屁。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560173076,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"51171ca00a3e9cd3399823522bb6835c","url_token":"yi-xiao-ran-45-88","name":"易小冉","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-95b1816c17b8a3eca078188b