":"zhang-zi-han-16-97","name":"无机化学下册","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1278f0d2e7a37b1a1fe0748f1cb893c4","user_type":"people","headline":"慎独","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559834433","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545787107,"updated_time":1545787107,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"先占个坑，1月1日来看(눈_눈)","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559819775,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b35445c9ef8469cc2ca5bfa9fd27ddcf","url_token":"123-15-65-82","name":"123","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b35445c9ef8469cc2ca5bfa9fd27ddcf","user_type":"people","headline":"学渣一枚","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559819775","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fdab6e27c4a4585f65e80b865efb644d_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785628,"updated_time":1545785628,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e证明了哥德巴赫猜想。。。嗯嗯嗯大概率我认为是错误的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        我先说明一下不是在嘲讽题主。想问一下题主学过数论没有。如果没有学过，那么证明肯定会有问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        如果作为高中生自学过数论，说明题主数学上平日成绩优异有空余时间钻研别的。建议好好学习，考个好大学或者去数学竞赛。没必要拿哥德巴赫猜想这种噱头混什么保送(坐等1月1日你论文发表再说)。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         顺便说一下这学期我们正好学数论，数论的难度我是有些了解的。。。。好难啊    \u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"559\" data-rawheight=\"332\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-959c0d85a1bb41494c47a98dc10f5df0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"559\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='559'%20height='332'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"559\" data-rawheight=\"332\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-959c0d85a1bb41494c47a98dc10f5df0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"559\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559806909,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"61e44c0aedf94929cc3ac32c9513424e","url_token":"zhu-jia-hao-28","name":"Mike","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/61e44c0aedf94929cc3ac32c9513424e","user_type":"people","headline":"画图狗","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559806909","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545784207,"updated_time":1545784425,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e请对数学保持应有的敬畏，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1上个好大学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2好好学习数学。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3证明猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1和2可以互换，直接跳过12就想做三。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e行吧，你可以的，中二少年  \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我在想，能证明猜想的人是不会问能否保送清华这类问题的，毕竟证明猜想一半的人已经做了教授了\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559776573,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b974ecdc63766bae3e2c8ea4368986c1","url_token":"gong-mi-52","name":"恭弥","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-baa9e84ffcdb55268863ba0b39bedb40_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-baa9e84ffcdb55268863ba0b39bedb40_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b974ecdc63766bae3e2c8ea4368986c1","user_type":"people","headline":"农学/模型/模拟器","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559776573","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545772140,"updated_time":1545772140,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e目光浅显到认为证明哥德巴赫猜想后考虑清北保送的孩子，你太小看数学了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e真正可以完美证明完这个的话，拿下菲尔兹奖不是问题。前人在这上边做了多少工作，用到了多少理论，你如果真的有研究有了解的话，目光早就该放在国外，明年就该出现在普林斯顿作报告了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559735131,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"bba1adad5112571a4ce18e9f3e2db38f","url_token":"li-long-yu-34","name":"Ergo Li","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhim